# Cloudflare R2 upload Worker (admin track upload)
# Deploy worker first; see cloudflare-worker/README.md
#
# Auth uses the current user's Firebase ID token, so no shared secret
# is needed in the frontend. The Worker validates that the user is an
# admin (users/{uid}.admin === true in Firestore) before issuing the
# upload URL.
VITE_R2_UPLOAD_ENDPOINT=https://fluxring-r2-uploader.<your-account>.workers.dev
